\begin_layout Section
Etymology
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At one point TriCovid becoming a separate project was considered a possibility.
 Portmanteaus were considered, however it felt morally dubious to do such
 a thing, as it may trivialise a serious situation.
 After a while TriCovid was chosen, as a harmless reference to the fact
 it displays three different metrics.
 When the request to separate was rejected the decision was made to keep
 the name, as TriCovid appears to be a very different experience when compared
 to the website.
\end_layout

